Unfortunately, screenshots or partial video records are not sufficient to appear on the leaderboard. A video of the full run is required.
We aknowledge recording full-game runs on mobile can be an issue and there are several ways to achieve that.
You can decrease the size of the file by using a recording app instead of the built-in recorder of your devide, with lowered quality settings. You can record without the audio, that's fine for this leaderboard. If the app produce several files, that's not an issue either, you can upload them separately on a dedicated hosting platform and then put every links to them in the form.
